\id ROM
\ide  UTF-8
\h Warumi 
\toc1 Warumi 
\toc2 Warumi 
\toc3 rom 
\mt1 Warumi  
\c 1
\cl Sura ya 1 
\p
\v 1 Ne Paulo, nembombi va Yesu Klisite yune nilaghiwe ukhusuhiwa, nukhulekhehana ne livagili lya Nguluve.  
\v 2 Ele lyu livangili ililyanchoviwe khatali na vouyamalango vamwene mumbusimbe uvuvalanche.  
\v 3 Nchinchova umwana va mwene, uveakholiwe mukhivumbukho ikhya Daudi khunjila eya mbili.  
\v 4 Umwene anchoviwe ukhuta Mwana va Nguluve khuu makha ga mepo umbanche khuluvoneklulo lwa vafwele, u Yesu Klisite Dada veto.  
\v 5 Khugendela umwene tupokhile uvupokhi wa kusuhiwa nu wedesi uwa lwidekho panie nekhe khelunga, khulitawa lya mwene.  
\v 6 Pagati pa khilunga ekhi, nayumwe mwelagiwe ukhuva va Yesu Klisite.  
\v 7 Ikalata eye ya mwevoni yumwe mtama khu va Rumi, vagane nu Nguluve, mwaelagiwe ukhuva vanu vavalanche. Ulukhugu luve kwenu, nu lugano ukhuma kwa Dada veto na khuswambe uYesu Klisite.  
\v 8 Mumbologolo nikhundemya uNguluve vago khwa Yesu Kliste khuliumwe mwevoni, ulwakhuva ulwedekho lulombeliliwa mukheluga vyoni.  
\v 9 Ulwakhuva u Nguluve isaidi vango, uvenikhumbombela ni numbula yango, kulimeyu ilya mwana va mwene, nduwu nitama ukhuvatambula.  
\v 10 Daima nchoni nidova muyesayo nchago ukhuta khujela iyavenchaga ninche nive numwe khukya khulya mwe.  
\v 11 Ninogwa ukhuvavona, ukhuta nevape efikhogelwa fya numbula, ninche nivayilenche.  
\v 12 Pwu ninogwa nekhave amakha paninie numwe, khunjila iya lwidekho lwa khila munu.  
\v 13 Lino valukholo, saninogwa mlemwe ukhulumanya ukhuta, ukhuta imesekhe mingi nesagile ukhincha khulyume, lenosesigiwe. Nikha nogwaga lino ukuva nisekhe khulyumwe ndawuyelekhu vanu ava khilunga.  
\v 14 Nidayiwa na vayunani na vahesya, avalemale na vapelwa.  
\v 15 Ulwakhuva une nilitayari ukhulumbelela elimenyu khulimwe nayumwe mwemulekhu Roma.  
\v 16 Ulwa khuva sanivona soni khulimeyu, ulwakhuva makha ga Nguluve ukhutopokha khukhila munu uveekhwedekha, khua vayahudi avakhwanda na khuva Yunani vope.  
\v 17 Ulwakhuva wayelweli wa Nguluve vuvonikhe ukhuma ulwedekho, mpauha ulwedekho, nduwuyesimbiwe, “Unya lwidikho itamaga nulwidikho.”  
\v 18 Ulwakhuva uvuhegi wa Nguluve vuvonikhe ukhuma kukhyanya ni mbivi nuvutola nogwa woni uwa vanu, uvuvivi wifikha uwayelweli.  
\v 19 Ulwakhuva, goni givonekha khwa Nguluve galipavuvalafu khuvene. Ulwakhuva uNguluve owavulile.  
\v 20 Imbombo ncha mwene enchosanchi vonekha vunonu nchivile pavuvalafu ukhuma khiliwa ulimwenguni. Khikwelevekha ukhugendela ifinu ifipeliwe. Imbombo incho makha ga mwene khihumana nu vufwa uwa khukhuma kuvutegulilo wa vuNguluve. Ukhuma, avanu ava viva vanchila vulegefu.  
\v 21 Ulwakhuva, va mayile uNguluve, savandolelage umwene khama Nguluve, savalikhusana, vavile vakhoyofu khumasage gavene, ni numbula nchavo incha vukhoyofu yaigile ekhisa.  
\v 22 Valikhwiyilaga veuiyaluhara, vakhava vapelwa.  
\v 23 Vakhalwandulania uvufwa wa Nguluve uvunchila vunagi khuvihwani khya munu uveanagikhe, ndiefidege, amakhanu akhayama lunde gane, ni fikhano ifikhwa fula.  
\v 24 U Nguluve akhavalekha vakhogage uvunogwe wa numbula nchavo imbivi, emivili givo kilikubediwa.  
\v 25 Na vene vayadwile elweli ya Nguluve ukhuva vudesi, valikhwesaya nu khugevombela imiguluve igige vakhandeka upelivavo, uviekhwi mekhiwa isikhu nchoni. Amina.  
\v 26 Ulwakuva, u Nguluve avalekhile vakhogage imbimbi nchavo enchiyasoni, ulwakhuva vaandulinie imbombo encha khatali vakha nchilekha incha khatali.  
\v 27 Vulevule, avagosi vakhanchilekha imbombo nchao ncha khatali khuvehe vavo nu khuva nu vuligu khuvene vavo. Ava vagosi khuva gosi ewavombaga inchi sancho nogelanile, valikhutole ulukoto khumbombo nchavo.  
\v 28 Ulwakhuva vabelile ukhuvanu Nguluve khuluhala lwavo, avalekhile vakhogage lyale, nchao imbivi, vavombage imbombo incho sanchinogelanile.  
\v 29 Vadigile nuvutulanogwa, uvuvivi, uvunogwe uvuvivi, vadigile uvunogwe, uvubudi, imbancha. Uvusyovi, na amasage amavivi.  
\v 30 Vavo vavile vasyovi, ava khehi navi khukalalila u Nguluve. Avayambancha, amatingo, ulwiginio, avene vavombo imbivi, nu vusavikhuva dwada avahonchi vavo.  
\v 31 Avene vanchila lukhala, savikhwidekha, vanchila lugano ulwa khwanda, vanchila lugano.  
\v 32 Vanchimayile indagilo ncha Nguluve, ukhuta vala avivombo imbombo incho, vanegiwa vabudiwe. Inave vivombo imbomob incho pwu viva vikhweelehana na vavo vivomba imbo incho.   
\c 2
\cl Sura ya 2 
\p
\v 1 Ule vovole uluhusa, yuve wikhega inungwa, ulyakhova yuve wikhega agavanino wikefunga yuve, ulyahuva yuwe wikhega wiwomba gagago.  
\v 2 Ulyahova tulumanyile khota uvokhegi wa Nguluve wayelyeli khuvavo vivomba amambo kama aga.  
\v 3 Uvewe usage uele, uvewikhega khuvawo vivomba imbombo incho nayove wiwomba amambo gagago. Poyowukhepa uvokhegi uwa Nguluve?  
\v 4 Apange wisaga sana khunyingi inchavombile uNguluve, ukhuncheliwa khuadhabu ya mwene, nuwovumefu wa mwene? sulumanyile ukhuta uvononu wamwene, wukhuhuvula khuhusayiwa?  
\v 5 Khuvogumu wa numbula yakho ugulevovole ulyesayo, wikhevehela yuve eakiba ya uwoheyi ukhisu uvukhegi khusihu yela yawo wonesiwa wa wokhegi yawolyeli ya Nguluve.  
\v 6 Umwene ikhopinchaga khela munu ekhepimo sava ninogwa ncha mwene.  
\v 7 Khuwawo valenowoyelweli na mambo amanonu vilonda esifa uludwado nukhunangekha, ikhuvapa uwomi wa sihu nchoni.  
\v 8 Kuvawo vihetenga, vavo savidwada uwoyelyeli vinogwa uhupoliwa uwukhegi nelyoyo elikali yikhwincha.  
\v 9 U Nguluve ayitwala etabu khumunu uyivomba imbivi, khunchandi tasi, numyuna tena  
\v 10 Ulyeginye, uvodyado eamani yikhuja khumunu iyivomba inonu, khumuyahudi na nyunani.  
\v 11 Uluva khosiholi ukhupendela, ulugano khya Nguluve.  
\v 12 Khuvange vakasinche ululagelo viyaga bila lulagelo, khuvale avange vakosije ukhukosa ulu lagelo, ayavikegiwa khululagelo.  
\v 13 Avavipoleka ululagelo avanya wolyeli kuvulongolu khwa Nguluve, vavo viwomba ululagolo yavivaleliwe uvuyelyeli.  
\v 14 Kuvanu vakelungu, avalevovole ululagelo vivomba kutabia ululagelo, avene vavile lulagelo kunumbula nchaivwo, avene valevovole ululagelo.  
\v 15 Yivoneka ukuta amambo khululagelo ghandechiwe igati munumbula nchavene. ezamili, yavene yikhovahega avene, amasage gavene vavo au ukhuvahega vikhuvedema vavo.  
\v 16 Nukhua Nguluve. Aga ayagikhomela khosihu inchiyaha ikhega inogwa ncha vanu voni, sawa nelimenyu lya mwene, khwa Yesu Klisite.  
\v 17 Tunchove tute wikheyelanga yuve myahudi, uyatamile mlulagele, usangelela ukhusifu uNguluve.  
\v 18 Ulumanye ulugano lya mwene, ukhupina amamba uguletofauti nago khuliho ukhulagenchiwa nu lulagelo.  
\v 19 Tunchove tute ulekhafu khuyuve vemwene ulendongoji khepofu, ulumuli khuvavo va lemuhisi,  
\v 20 uyisahihisya avanchila lohola, umanyisi va vana, nukhuta ulenalyo ululagelo nuvumanyisi uwayelyeli.  
\v 21 Yuve, vukhondombelela uyunge sawihemanyisa yove? Yuve wilombelela ukhuhencha, uveve savukhencha?  
\v 22 Yuve winchova ukhuta savuvomba uvuligu, savuvomba? yuve wikalala ekhehwani, savuhencha khukanisa?  
\v 23 Yuve wikheginya khululagelo, savuhonyongonyola u Nguluve khwa hudenya ululagelo?  
\v 24 Khulimenyu lya Nguluve eliwenyu linangekha huvanu va kelunga husababu yeto,” ndowayandikhiwe.  
\v 25 Ukhuhakikisiwa khwawoyelyeli hunogiwa ungakongongage ululagelo, ungawe savukonga ululagelo, ukhoha khwaho khwivasio khwohoha.  
\v 26 Angave umunu asayiwe, ikhwendelela ukhwibala ululagelo, ukhwesaya khwa mwene hiwva sahuvoneha ukhuta ikwesaya.  
\v 27 Nu mwene iyikhwesaya khuasili alalakhegiwa angatimesye ululagelo? Uwo wosimbe uwaandekhiwe ne tohara bado ulesaliti va lulagelo.  
\v 28 Umwene sio myahudi uya vile vahonji, uhutahiliwa sio khuahonji tu kumbele.  
\v 29 Umwene Myahudi uva gati ne, tyesoyo lya gati, munumbula sio ndimenyu, ulyeginyo ulya saluhumana na vanu lyukhoma kwa Nguluve.   
\c 3
\cl Sura ya 3 
\p
\v 1 Pwu Myahudi ikhava khehi? Ukhukhekhetiwa khwikhava khehii?  
\v 2 Lononu fincho khela njela. Khuvwutengulilo, avayahudi vapevilwe ulovonekhelo ukhukhuma khwa Nguluve.  
\v 3 Pwu yayiva ndeti ingave Avayahudi avange valevovole ulwedekho? ukhu sitakhwedekha khwavene khukhokhovekha uvugolofu wa Nguluve ukhuva vovivi?  
\v 4 Ate padebe, ulwa khuva, nndekhe Nguluve avonekhe ukhuta va yelweli, ndayeve khela munu nn'desi. Ingave umuyasimbiwe, “Ukhuta pwu uvonekhe ukhuva ulevayelweli mu mamenyu gaakho, ukhulotelela vwuvukhwingela pa vukhegi.  
\v 5 Engave imbivi nchetu nchivonesya elweli eya Nguluve, pwu tute khekhi? uNguluve si mbivi vwu ikhumya elyoyo lya mwene khukhuta ale evo? Ninchova ukhukhumana na lweli yavwu munu.  
\v 6 Ate! ndakhekhi u Nguluve umuyakhiva ikhikhekhega ekhilunga?  
\v 7 Engave lweli ya Nguluve ukhugendela uvwodesi vwango ikhumia ulwiginio khu mwene, khekhi nipi khegiwa ndu ntula nongwa?  
\v 8 Khekhi tunchove ndu vovya tudeteliwa na avange vikhwedekhana ukhuta twinchova, “Tuvombe imbivi, pwu ginche amananu? Uvukhegi khuvene vwa yelweli.  
\v 9 Khenu khehi? Ukhwetetela yofwe? Losikhuli, ulwa khuva ufwe tuvadetile avayahudi na Wayunani voni paninie, ukhuta vale pasi pa mbivi.  
\v 10 Ele ndavovwalesimbiwe: Asikhiwi uvayelweli, nu uve aliyumo.  
\v 11 Asikhuli umunu yuywa ikhweliwa. Asikhuli umunu uveikhondonda u Nguluve.  
\v 12 Voni vasyetwikhe, voni paninie wakhosinche ulwedekhano. Asikhuli uveivomba inonu na aleomo.  
\v 13 Emisingo gya vene vuguli uvole mwanchi. Indimi incha vene nchidetile, ugoda gwa njokha guli pasi mumilomo gya vene.  
\v 14 Emilomo gya vene gedekhile ulukhoto nu luvavo.  
\v 15 Amalunde ga vene ginyilela ukhududa ukhisa.  
\v 16 Uvunangi nu vukhuvilwa filimnjila ncha vene.  
\v 17 Avanu ava savayemanyile enjela ya lweli.  
\v 18 Lusimuli uludwado lwa Nguluve pa mikho gavo.”  
\v 19 Leno tulumanyile ukhuta khyokyoni ekhenchoviwa nu lulagelo, khinchova khuvavo valepasi palulagilo pwu khela ndomo gudendiwe, pwu ekhelunga khyoni khendondage u Nguluve.  
\v 20 Ulwa khuva gusipali umbeli uguyakheva guvaleliwa vwa yelweli khu mbombo ncha lulagelo khu mwene. Ulwa khuva ukhugendela mu lukhwincha ulukhala lwa mbivi.  
\v 21 Ulwa khuva leno bila lulagelo, elweli ya Nguluve yemanyikhikhe, yavonikhe khululagelo lwa vanya malango.  
\v 22 Eye yu lweli ya Nguluve ukhugendela elweli eya Yesu klisite khuvavo vikhumwedekha.  
\v 23 Ulwa khuva voni vavombile imbivi nu khuva nu uvuvalanche vudebe uvwa Nguluve.  
\v 24 Vavaleliwe uvwayelweli vulevule khu lukhungu lwa mwene khu njila iya vupokhi vuvwa vule mwa Klisite Yesu.  
\v 25 Ulwa khuva u Nguluve ang'ominche u Klisite Yesu ave lusayano khu njila ya yelweli mu nkhisa gwa mwene. Ang'ominshe Klisite ndu ntangeli va yelweli eya mwene, ukhunchisye khela inongwa inchilutile.  
\v 26 Pa khwiyumilincha pamwene aga gone gakhumile pwu elweli ya mwene yevonekhe khu misekhe ege. Eye yale pwu ivonesye uvwa yelweli vwa mwene, pwu livonekhe ukhuta ikhombalela umunu alavenchaga elweli mwa Klisite.  
\v 27 Pwu khulindakhu ukhwiginia? khulekhekhine khu mbombo ilekhu? Ulutu lwa mbombo? Ate, ulutu lwa yelweli.  
\v 28 Pwu tumalela ukhuta umunu ivaleliwa elweli khu luhungu hetavomba imbombo incha lulagilo.  
\v 29 Tute uNguluve avile Nguluve va Wayahudi vene? Umwene savile Nguluve va vanu va khilunga khyoni? Eena va khilunga khyoni.  
\v 30 Yengave ya lweli u Nguluve aleyomo, alavavalela elweli avakhekhetiwe huluhungu, na vavo savakhekhetiwe khu njila eya luhungu.  
\v 31 Pwu ufwe tukhulwandula ululagilo lwa luhungu, ate ufwe tukhulwedekha ululagilo.   
\c 4
\cl Sura ya 4 
\p
\v 1 Twichova khikhi khwa Abrahamu, ubaba veto khunjila ya mbili, avomnikhe?  
\v 2 Pakhuva u Abrahamu avalilewe ei lweli khunjila ya mbombo akhali eva nekhinu kya khwigin'wa sio khumiho ga Nguluve.  
\v 3 UAbrahamu amuidikhe u Nguluve akha valili wa ei lweli ukhuva lweli.  
\v 4 Lino khumunu uvivomba ei mbombo uluhombo lwa mwene saluvaliwa ukhuva lusayo, ila gwiva ikole.  
\v 5 Nakhumunu uvivomba ei mbombo nukhumwidikha ula viavaheliwe ei lweli, yuywa sio igolofu, ulwidekho lwa munu uywa luvalili wa ukhuva haki.  
\v 6 U Daudi vope inchova ulusayo pakianya pamunu uvi uyu u Nguluve ambalile ei lweli khunjila ya mbombo.  
\v 7 Achovile, “Vasayiwe vala avaimbivi ncha vene n'chisekheliwe nisambi n'cha vene n'chigube khiliwe.  
\v 8 Asayiwe umunu ula uvi u Nguluve sikhu mbalila uvutula nongwa.  
\v 9 Puulusayo ulu lwa vanu ava keketwe vene, emo khuvala avasava keketiwe, pakhuvatwi n'chova, khwa Abrahamu ulwidikho lwa mwene luvaliliwe ukhuva lweli.”  
\v 10 Pu avaliliue ndeti vu badusu keketiwe, ewo vusaakeketiwe? Salemumbu kegete vu badu sakeketiwe.  
\v 11 U Abrahamu apokhile alama hwani eikhwa khusita ukhu keketiwa gula gwali ei ng'uli gwa vuvilweli wa lwidekho uluale nalo tayari, vabadu sakeketiwe uluvonekhelo ulu vale njila ya khuvonekha ukhuva baba va voni. Avi khwidikha hata ndava ngave badu sava keketiwe.  
\v 12 Eyi yavonisye ukhuva uAbrahamu avombikhe ukhuva baba va vukeketie sio khuvala tu avavinogwa ukhu keketiwa bakhoila kuvala avavikhu n'chi konga ingendele n'cheto n'cha baba vito u Abrahamu. nulu lwidekho uluake nalwo khuvala ava savakeketiwe.  
\v 13 Pakhuva salwale lulagilo ululwa home n'chiwe khwa Abrahamu na vana va mwene, ulwidehano ulu salwale ukhuta viva nuvu halie wa khilunga, ila lwale ukhugendela ei lweli ya lwidiko.  
\v 14 Eingave vala ava ndagilo vuva vu hale, ulwidiko lwiva lusipali ei ahadi yave yebadelekhe.  
\v 15 Pakhuva indagilo n'chileta uluvipo, pakhuva pala upu ululagilo ukhupulikha khu sikhuli.  
\v 16 Khunjila eiye luleta ulwidikho ili luve khukhisa, pwu ululagilo ulu lwiva pavuvalafu pakhi vumbukho khoni navaholiwa ava sio vala avan'chi manyile eindagilo, ila vala ava lwidekho lwa Abrahamu. Pakhuva umwene vibaba veto twivoni.  
\v 17 Pakhuva vegiwe ei lwakhuta ni khukhuvikha u veve ukhuva baba vavingi ukhu konga khila eikhinchoviwe u Abrahamu ale uvo, pande waula ava amwidikhe yaani uNguluve uvikhuvapa avafyile uwomi nukhugavikha agasipaliukhwa pugale.  
\v 18 Paninei nicho n'choni n'cha khunje, u Abrahamu ale nuvu kifu amwidikhe uNguluve khusikhu n'chi khwincha akhava baba va vanu vingi, ukhukongana na khila ekhi n'choviwe,” Vuyiva khukhi vumbukho kyakho.  
\v 19 Umwene ale pepe ndwidiko. UAbrahamu aidikhe ukhuva umbele gwa mwene yuywa gwa silile ukhu fya, ale ne miakha mia yimo. Pia alikubaliana na hali ya kufyakwa litumsu lwa Sara.  
\v 20 Ulwakhuva uNguluve alagile, uAbrahamu akhava mwidehin'chi akha va amagha mundweidikho nukhuginwa uNguluve.  
\v 21 Alumanyile ukhuta kila eikya lagile uNguluve alei nuvuwesyo uwa khutimesya.  
\v 22 Eiye yuya vahiwe khumwene ukhuva lweli.  
\v 23 Sio gasimbiwe ukhuva faida ya mwene ukhuvaliliwa khumwene.  
\v 24 Lwasimbiwe khwaajili yeto, nakhuvala ava avavavaliliwe ei mbalelo nufye avavikhwidekha ukhuta an'chusinche udada vito uYesu Klisite ukhuma khuvana avafule.  
\v 25 Uyu viula uvi ahumenchiwe khunjila ya nongwa ncheto, nukhunchusiwa ili tukave ukhuvali hiwa ei lweli.   
\c 5
\cl Sura ya 5 
\p
\v 1 Ulwakhuva tuvalilive khuuchila iyalwidikho tulinulwi elikho ulwidikho nu Nguluve munjila ya Ntwa vitu uYesu Klisite.  
\v 2 Ukhugendela inchila iyi na yufwe tulinusikhi ugwa lwidikho nu luhungu mugati nukwima. Tuhovokha nu vunonu uvu ikhutupa uNguluve khusikhi, uvunonu uwakhulundamana, imbuvalanche uwa Nguluve.  
\v 3 Ulwakhuva tuhovokha nu vukhuvilwa weto tukhulumanya ukhuta uvukhuvilwa wihola uvugatalufu.  
\v 4 Uvugatalufu wihola ukwidikhiwa nu khwidika ukhuhola uvukhifu uwa nsikhi.  
\v 5 uvukhifu uvu savugatala ulwakhuva ulugano ulwa Nguluve lududiwe munumbula nchito ukhugendela mumepo umbalanche, uvya huminche khulyufwe.  
\v 6 Uputwale vapepe khusikhi ugu mwa Klisite afwile khunanya mbivi.  
\v 7 Yiva ng'afu ukhufwa uwuno umo uviifwa nu wayilweli alekhe ukhufwa umunu unonu.  
\v 8 Lugave ulugano edikhile yuywa ukhutwale vanya sambi, iyi ng'afu yumo ukhufu khu nyalwidikho.  
\v 9 Ukhuva khugoni tuvaliwe nu suyilweli mukhisa gwa mwene twipona ukhuhuma khuluvipo ulwa Nguluve.  
\v 10 Usikhi ugutwale nu ndugu, u Nguluve, uNguluve akhatusyikhila khu nchila iya vufwe, uwa mwana va mwene, pasikhi ugu amalile ukhutusyikhila akhatupokha nu vutamo wito.  
\v 11 Lino syo nduvu, pu tuhekhela nu Nguluve ukhugendela khutwa u Yesu Klisite, umwene uvi lino twupilile uvugatalufu uvu.  
\v 12 Lino ukhugendela mumunu imbivi nchaingile mukhilunga khunchela iya vufwe, nu vufwe vukhalutilila khu vanu voni, ulwakhuva voni vavombi isambi.  
\v 13 Ipakha lino ululagilo, lwa nogwa wale wa nkhilunga, lino imbivi sanjivaliwa vivusikhi ugwa lulagilo lusikhuli.  
\v 14 Na vulevule uvufwe ukhuhuma khwa nyakhatale u Adamu ipakha usikhi u gwa Mose, khuvala avasavavombe imbivi, ukhusita ukhwidika uvuvivi akhale ikhwincha, vingi va fwile khukhisa kya Nguluve nu vunonu wa khisa wa munu, Yesu Klisite vulutilile ukhulutilila khuvingi.  
\v 15 Uvunonu twupilile vuvule khuvuvwi, ulwa khuva uvutulanogwa uwayumo vingi vafyile, vuvule khu khisa khya Nguluve nu khutupa uvunonu mukhisa vuvule ikhya munu yumo, u Yesu Klisite ilutilile khuvingi.  
\v 16 Ukhusana sakhulihewuile ndu muwu uvyavombile imbivi. khuluvafu ulunge uvuhigi nu lukhungu lwa inchile uluvofu ulunge, ikhi khungilwa kya vuvule, ikhihihuma ukhuvaliliwa nu vulweli wainchile mvimbuvivi.  
\v 17 Uvulweli wa imbivi incha vufwe uwa munu umu wa endelile ukhulutilila na vala avikhwupilila uluhungu ulwingi pupavunye ni khikhungiwa ikyalweli vikhikhungiwa ukhugendela mumivele igwa Yesu Kliste.  
\v 18 Linu ingave inogwa incha yuwu ni ncha vanu voni vainjile khuhigiwa, ukhugendela mumbombo yimo iya lweli satwavaliliwe mumbili ugwa lweli mumbanu voni.  
\v 19 Ulwakhuva ukhugendela mumunu nu khusita ukhwidikha yumu, vingi vavombeliwe inongwa, ugendela ukhusita ukhwidika khwa yumo nu khuvikha na lweli.  
\v 20 Lino ululagilo lwaingile pupaninye ni mbivi ukhuta njendelelage. Nu vuvivi wolikhuongesekha, na uluhungu lwope lulikhwongesekha.  
\v 21 Iyi yahumile ukhuta isambi umunchongesikhe, nu khufwa, khukhuta ikisa khiwesya ukhulutilila ukhugendela muvulweli ni mivele khigieto khusikhu njoni ukhugendela mupokhi u Yesu Klisite Utwe veto.   
\c 6
\cl Sura ya 6 
\p
\v 1 Khumbe tunchove khihi? Tughendelelage ukhuvomba imbivi ukhuta ulusayo lyongelele?  
\v 2 Bakhoo. Ufwe twafwile mumbivi, tuwesya ndakhikhi, ukhutama umwa khange?  
\v 3 Tee samulumanyile ukhuta vala avonchiwe mwa Klisite vaonchiwe mumbufwe wa mwene?  
\v 4 Twasyieliwa pupaninie nu mwene ukhughendela khulwonoho mumbufwe. Ile lyavombike ukhuta u Klisite waghiniwe ukhuma khuvufwe ukhughendele uvutwa wa Dada, ukuta nayufwa tuwesyaghe ukhughenda mumbupya wa khutama.  
\v 5 Ulwakhuva tuhungile pupaninie nu mwene khukhihwani kya vufwe uwamwene, pwu tulahanga pupaninie mumbunchuka uwamwene.  
\v 6 Ufwe tulumanyile ndee uvumunu wietu uwakhatale wavungiwe pupaninie nu mwene, ukhuta umbile ugwa mbivi ghunangeikhage eile lyahumile ukhuta tulekhe ukhuva vasuhiwa va mbivi.  
\v 7 Umwene uvyafwile aviekhiwe ukhuva vayilweli ukhukongana ni mbivi.  
\v 8 Ukhuva tufwile pupaninie nu Klisite, tukwidikha ukhuta tutamaga pupaninie nu mwene.  
\v 9 Tulumanyi ukhuta uYesu anchukhile ukhuma khuvufwe, nukhuta samunu uvyafiwile tena. Uvufwe savukhunkonga kavile.  
\v 10 Khuvufwe uwafyelile khu nongwa incha mbivi, afyile khamo ukhuvafyela voni. Nakhukhutama ukhuitama, itama mumakha nga Nguluve.  
\v 11 Khunjila iyo yiyiyo, nayumwe khulondiwa avanu avafwile ukhuva avanu avafwile mumbivi, ulwakhuva kwa Nguluve mwa Yesu Klisite.  
\v 12 Kwu baako ukhuta ukhunogwa kwa mbieli khulekhe ukhukwile imbivi ukhuta umbilie gwukongage umuguunogela uvunonu uwakhunogwa.  
\v 13 Ulekhe ukhughava uluvafu lwa mbili gwakho khumbivi nifivombelo ifisafinogiwa, pwu twihumiaghe yufwe khwa Nguluve, nda vumi avahumile kwa Nguluve.  
\v 14 Tulekhe ukhuta imbivi ukwutumilila, ulwakhuva samliepasi pa fyombo ifya lweli kwa Nguluve.  
\v 15 Khikhi khumbe? Tuvombe imbivi ulwakhuva tulipasi pa ndageilo, ila pasi palusayo? Kwu bakho.  
\v 16 Samulumanyile ukhuta khumwene yuywa uviikhuminche yuywa ukhuva imbombi vei mwene umwe mulivavombi va mwene, umwene vipanogile ukhumpulikhincha? Iye lweli nupwu mungave umwe mulivavomba mbivi inchikhuvahilika khuvufwe, apange mlivasuhiwa avakwidikila ukuvahilika kuvufwe, apange mlievasuhiwa va wayilweli.  
\v 17 Pwu aginiwagwe uNguluve! ulwakhuva mukhale vavombi va mbivi, ulwakhuva mwidikhe ukhuma munumbula ukhukongana nulumanyisyo ulumwapokhile.  
\v 18 Muviekhiwe mumbwavukhe ukhuhuma kwumbivi, khange muvikhiwe vavombi va vuyilweli.  
\v 19 Ninchova ndumunu ulwakhuva yavudekhe dekhe wa mivile gyitu. Ulwakhuva mukhahuminchi mumivili gyinyo ukhuva vasuhiwa vayilweli kuvu vanche.  
\v 20 Upwumukha vasuhiwa va mbivi, mukhale mbuleghefu pavutali ni lweli.  
\v 21 Kwuu nsieki ugwa mkha ni niesekhe yilikhu kwu kumbombo iyumukhuyivona leino mwivona soni khuieyo? ulwakhuva khuvusilo wa mbombo incho wiwa vufwe.  
\v 22 Ulwakhuva lino vavavikhile mumbwa vokhe khuvutali ni mbivi na muvikhiwe vasuhiwa kwa Nguluve, mlieniseke mbuvalanche. Khuvusililo uwumi wasikunchoni.  
\v 23 Ulwakhuva uvivomba imbivi iekhigavilo kya mwene uvufwe, khange iekhikhungilwa ikya vuvule ikya Nguluve uwumi uwa kusila lusiku mwa Yesu Klisite untwe vetu.   
\c 7
\cl Sura ya 7 
\p
\v 1 Au samulumanyile, valokolo lwango (olwakhuva nijova na vanu avalumanyile urulagero), khukhuta urulagero lukhundo ngoja umunu vobado inkafu?  
\v 2 Olwakhuva udala avatoliwe akungiwe nululagelo khwa gosi va mwene, vunkafu mave ogosi va mwene ifiwa iva avikhilwe ukhuva mwavukhe ukhukhuma na nurulagero lwa khutolana.  
\v 3 Nevetwita, osekhe ugosi va mwene witama, inave nogosi uyunge, ikhelangiwa indigu, inave ogosi va mwene afwele, iva mwuvukhe nululagero, evo siva ndigu angave itama nu gosi uyunge.  
\v 4 Ulwakhuva, valokolo lwango, umwe mwavombiwe ukhuva wafwe nurulagero khu njila iya Klisite. Evilendete uhutama pupaninie nu ninoo, khu mwene uyakhanchukhile ukhukhuma khu vufwe ili tuwesye ukhung'olela u Nguluve isekhe.  
\v 5 Ulwakhuva vutukhale pa hali iyambele, uvunogwe uwambivi fikhasi simwile ifikhancho fweto khunjila iya lugalero nukhu vuholela uvufwe isekhe.  
\v 6 Ulwakhuva tudenduliwe ukhukhuma mu rulagelo. Tuyefwelile iyekhube jekhana. Ili tuvoese ukhuvombekhe uvupya mwa mepo, nufwe uwahatale uwa vusimbe.  
\v 7 Tutekhekhi? ululagero ulwa mbivi? La hasha. Inave evoo, sananikhulumanya imbivi, waleusite ukhuva munjila iya lulagero. ulwakhuva sananikhulumanya ukhuno gwa inave ululagero salwalwinchoova, “Olekhe okhonogwa.”  
\v 8 Olwakhova imbivi nchapeviwe indagero nu khuleta igati indyu ne khela namna iya khunogwa. Ulwakhuva imbivi khesita rulagelo nchifwile.  
\v 9 Nayune nale mwumi pavulongonchi uwa ndagero, upuyainchilem dagero, imbivi nchapewiwe uwumi, one nafwe.  
\v 10 Ululagero ululwale lwa khukhu khelekhela uwumi lwapendwi khe ukhuva vufwe khulwune.  
\v 11 Ulwakhuva imbivi nchapeviwe akhavalelo pa lulagero ulwa vudesi. Ukhugendela ululagero, nafwile.  
\v 12 Leno ululagero luvalanche, ulwakhuva indagero nchivalanchiwe, yalweli nu vusalaama.  
\v 13 Ulwa khuva iyiyale nonu khulwune wale vufwe khulwune? Isite ukhuva eve mwee. Ulwakhuva imbivi, ili yevonekhe ukhuta mbivivi yinogiwa yegendele munonu, yevekhu uwufu igati ndyune. Yale ukhugendela ululagero imbivi nchikhwendelela ukhuva sinchoo.  
\v 14 Ulwa khuva tulumanyile ukhuta imbivi nchikhuma nukhutengulile munumbula ulwakhuva one nelemunu va mbele. Nigonchiwe pasi pa vulongonchi mwambivi.  
\v 15 Ulwakhuva ilenivomba, sanikhweliwa liwa hoeli. Ulwakhuva eleninogwa ukhuvomba, sanivomba, na ele elekalalile, lwuelyo elenivomba.  
\v 16 Ulwakhuva nengavombe elesani nogwa, nikhwedekhana nululagero ukhuta ululagero lunonu.  
\v 17 Ulwakhuva sio nene ne nikhogo avombela ago, ulwakhuva nchu mbivi inchinchilekhulwune igati.  
\v 18 Ulwa khuva nelumanyile ukhuta igati ndyune, ila sanikhule vombela.  
\v 19 Ulwakhuva elinonu eleninogwa soni khulevombela, ila elivivi ele saninogwa lwunikhulevombela.  
\v 20 Leno kama nivomba elesanino gwa, sinene yune nikhulevomba, ulwakhuva yu yila embivi iyeyitama igati ndyune.  
\v 21 Nelumanyile, mwele indagero igati ndyune iyakhunogwa ukhuvomba amanonu, ulwakhuva uvovivi nuvule igati ndyunee.  
\v 22 Ulwakhuva nikhurukhovokhela ululagero ulwa Nguluve igati ndyune.  
\v 23 Ulwakhuva nivona imbinu inchiilivonge muvikhanjo ifya mbele ugwango. Yietova hubancha embombe enya eyahekhara lwango. Yikhumbikha une neledovwava mbivi inchili vikhancho ifyambele gwango.  
\v 24 Une nele munu va lukuto! veve ni uyaha ikhonyokhora nu mbile ogu ugwa vufwe?  
\v 25 Inave ukhu mwale khwa Nguluve nu Yesu Klisite umbaha vetu! Leno. One nemwene nulukhala lwango nikho lovombela ululagelo ulwa Nguluve. Pakhuva, khumbile nikhunchivombela embombo imbivi.   
\c 8
\cl Sura ya 8 
\p
\v 1 Yesipali ehukumu ya viboko havalemwe Yesu Klisite.  
\v 2 Uhuva eshelia ya numbula ya hukianya hwa Yesu Klisite yembwene une nivile hulu ni mbivi nuvufwe.  
\v 3 Uhuva eshelia yichile mbali ni mbivi yalemilwe uhuvomba uhuva naamu umbile uNguluve avombile asuhile umwana yumo avenesadaha eya mbivi ahayehega embivi ya mbivi.  
\v 4 Avombile ivo masuhano ga ndagelo yetimizwe igati yeto ugwe tusite uhukonga umbile lakini avavikonga enumbula.  
\v 5 Vavo vikonga umbile visaga amambo gambile leno avikonga amambo ganumbula vovi saga amambo ganumbula.  
\v 6 Uhuva amalengo gambile ga vufwe bali ama lengo ganumbula uwavuhe.  
\v 7 Uhuva amalengo gambile gale nuhukalala nu Nguluve uhuva sayihedeha idagelo icha Nguluve wala sayiwesie uhudeha.  
\v 8 Vala avikonga umbele saviwe sia uhugana uNguluve.  
\v 9 Hata leno samlehumbeli bali mlehunumbula kama mle hunumbula mutama gati lakini kama mle hunumbula mutama gati lakini kama munu alebila nembula ya Klisite uywa sio vamwene.  
\v 10 Kama uKlisite alegati ndiomwe umbele gufwile humambo ga mbivi bali numbula yeehige nonu.  
\v 11 Uhuva enumbala ya yula uvia chusiche uYesu uhuhuma huvufwe itama gati mliomwe yuywe achu siche uYesu Klisite uhuhuma huvufwe wamivele gienyo egi vufwe uvi tama munumbula chenyo.  
\v 12 Ululeno valukololiwanga ufwe tulenu kole, lakini uvwe tutamaa simbile.  
\v 13 Kama tutama numbile mle kalibu uhufwa lakini umnave hunumbula mwiviha engendelo ulwa mbilemtama.  
\v 14 Nduvovi vibuwo nsoswa ne numbula ya Nguluve avo vuvana va Nguluve.  
\v 15 Uhuva samwa pohele inumbula ya mateso ate uhuduada badala mwapohile enumbula yahuva vana tulela, “Abba, Baba!”  
\v 16 Enumbula yeyeni yehwelewa pamoja ne numbula pahuva tule vana va Nguluve.  
\v 17 Tunave tulevana tulisile hwa Nguluve uvwe tulisili pamoja nu Klisite tunave tuteseha nu Klisite ili tupate uhuginiwa nu mwene.  
\v 18 Uhuva ni valela amateso agawakati uvu uhuva ufwe twelungile nuvuvaha uwa tuvonehile huliufwe.  
\v 19 Uhuva iviumbe fioni vilola yuywa uhuvoneha kuvana ava Nguluve.  
\v 20 Uhuva uvuumbaji wavombiwe nnbiki sio huhiali yeto ilakwa sababu yayuywa na hutesemela.  
\v 21 Uvuvumbaji uwa mwenye vulavehiwa huru nuhuhuma humateso ga vuvivi nu hwingila mbovuhulu wa vana va Nguluve.  
\v 22 Uhuva tuhwelewa uvuvumaji nuhuteseha nuvu chungu hata leno.  
\v 23 Siyo yufwe tuliona malipuko ya numbula ufwe tutamwa hunafasi cheto vutugojela uhu vombiwa humivele gieto.  
\v 24 Uhuva twa pohiwe lakini ehenu hihio nekonihe uhuva nehe wene vani ugojela ehehivoneha?  
\v 25 Bali tuhuhepulehela tuhegojela kwa saburi.  
\v 26 Hunjela yeyeyo enumbula yope yehututana uvusaifu weto uhuva samanyile usaya jinsi umyinogela uhwesaya lakini enumbula yihutudavela huhwa sahudoveha.  
\v 27 Na mwene uviichungusiva inumbu uhuyelewa uluhala lwa numbula sababu vidova huniaba ya vene ava vihwamini idova huniaba yao vaamini humapenzi ga Nguluve.  
\v 28 Nufwe tuhelewa wote avaganile uNguluve umweneivomba embombo pamoja huvunonu huvanu avihelangiwa humalengo gwa mwene.  
\v 29 Husababu voni ava avavamanyile tangu hatale na avacheguile tangu hatale vahwanane nufuno ugwa mwana va mwene i umwene aholiwe ave vya hunza miongoni mwovalukolo vingi.  
\v 30 Na vala avavachagwile ako avelangile navala avavela ngile avavalile uvuyeleli navala avavalile uvuyelweli avo avaginiche.  
\v 31 Tuchove hehe juu mambo aga? uNguluve angave uvupate weto veni uvale hukianya huliufwe?  
\v 32 Uvepila sihundeha umwana va mwene bali ahuniche huzili yeto tuvanu twevoni iweza uhu kosia uhutu tanga na mambo goni pamoja nufwe?  
\v 33 Veni uve ilvesia uhuva sitaha uNguluve vemwene ihuva valela uvuye lweli.  
\v 34 Veni uvepia ihukahega adhabu? Klisite Yesu veafule hu ajili yetu nuhuvahuago umwene alifufuka umwene itavala mahali pa heshima na tena viihuto dovela.  
\v 35 Veni uve ihutu gava nuvugane uwa Klisite Yesu etabu, au amateso, au enjala au hebwinda au hatali au emundu?  
\v 36 Kama umoyasimbiwe kwa faida yaho tuifwa imsi yoni twavaleliwe kama ngosi ya hubudiwa.”  
\v 37 Katika mambo ufwe tule vasiti vavasindi katika yeya uvatu ganile.  
\v 38 Uhuva na malile uhukela kwamba wala uvufwe wala uludeva wala usuhiwa wala mamlaka wala ifinu ifilipo wala ifinu vivyozavyo wala amaha,  
\v 39 Wala agalehukianya wala agale pasi wala kiumbe hio hioni sahehaweswe uhutugava nulugano la Nguluve ambaye ve Klisite Yesu utwa veto.   
\c 9
\cl Sura ya 9 
\p
\v 1 Ninchova icha yelweli mwa Klisite. Saninchova uvudesi, ni nyievonelo nchengo nchikhumbula paninie nune mumepo umbalanche,  
\v 2 Ukhuta khulinulusu valo uluvaha nuluvavo ulusalwisila ngati munumbula yango.  
\v 3 Ukhuta nale ninogwe une nie mwene ukhukotoliwa nu khutengiwa patali nu Klisite khunogwa ya valokolo lwango, uvuvahwani nune khimbili.  
\v 4 Avene vanya Israeli, uvalivumbikhe vana, va vuvalanche, nu lwokhelo lwa lutagilo, ukhwisa ya khwa Nguluve nu lwokhelo.  
\v 5 Avene vuvalongonchi u Klisite wa inchile kwu lisima ukhofwala umbili ugu - umwene vi Nguluve va fyoni. Navope agini vwage imiaka. Amina.  
\v 6 Khange sakhukhuta ulwidihano lwa Nguluve lukemilwe ukhutimila. Ulwakhuva sakhilo munu uviavile inya Israeli vi muIsrael lweli.  
\v 7 Ate ne khikhipapo kya Abrahamu ukhuva vana va mwene lweli, “Pwu ukhugendela kwa Isaka ikhipago kyoko khikhwelangiwa.”  
\v 8 Ukhuta avana va mbili savana va Nguluve. Pwu avanu va lwidihano viloliwa ukhuva khipapo.  
\v 9 Uhwakhuva ili lyu limenyu lya lwidiheno: “Mwu misinkhi haya nikhwincha, nu Sara iva nu mwana.”  
\v 10 Salili vuvule, nayu Rebeka ukhukhava unchigo khu munu yumo, u Isaka udada vitu-  
\v 11 Ukhuta avana vakhasigalile ukhu holiwa khange sakha vomba imbombo yoyoni inonu apange imbivi, apange uvunogwe wa Nguluve ukhukongana nu vuhale wime, sio khu mbombo, ulwakhuva ukuta.  
\v 12 Lyanchovile khu mwene, “Umbaha ikhumbombela udebe.”  
\v 13 Nduvuyisimbiwe: U Yakobo naaganile, pwu Esau ansulile.”  
\v 14 Pwu lino pwu twinchova ikhikhi? Khuli vuvivi khwa Nguluve? Ata.  
\v 15 Ulwakuva inchova kwa Mose, “Niva nikhisa kwulo uvinikwu nsyikhela, niva nu lusyikhilo kwa ula uviya nikwu n'syikhila, khange niva huruma khu yule uvinikwusyikila.  
\v 16 Pwu lino sayivile umwene uviinogwa khange sa lwakuva inyile uviivonesya ikhisa.  
\v 17 Ulwakuva uvusimbe vwita kwa Farao, “Khuvunogwe uvu uvuvamana nikha khwimikha une nivonesye amakha gango khulyuve, nukuva ilitavwa lyango linchovivwage ikhilunga kyoni.”  
\v 18 Pwu lino uNguluve iva ni khisa khumunu yoni uvyaganile, na uvyaganile, ikhumbikhe ukhuvanya ngani.  
\v 19 Pwu yawita khulione, “Pwu khikhi vupilola uvuvivi? Pwu alikhi uviegumilinche uvunogwe vwa mwene?”  
\v 20 Vi munu veve veni vi vukhumbulo vunge uNguluve? vwiwesya ukhulumanye ikhinu ikyu vumbile ukunchova kwu munu uvya khivumbile, “Khekhi ukhambikhile evwo une?”  
\v 21 Khukhu uvivumba inchila vwa yelweli kwu ng'anga ukhuvumba ikhivombelo ukhumana nu ng'anga gula gule, ni khyombo khinge khu mbombo yi figono fyoni?  
\v 22 Ndakhekhi ingave, uNguluve, uvi alinuvunu vwa khuvonesya uvuvivi vwa uvuvivi vwa mwene nu khuvomba ne makhaga mwene ukhuvoneka, akhanogile ukwiyumilinche, iatbu iyuyivikhiwe kwa khuyancho?  
\v 23 Ndakhikhi ingave avombile evo avonesye uwingi vwa vulancha vwa mwene kwu fyombo fya khisa, ifyo ifi fikhavikhilwe kwu vuvalanche?  
\v 24 Ndakhikhi ingave akhavombile khuvanu va khilunga?  
\v 25 Nduvwichova khange khwa Hosea: “Nikhuvilanga avanu vango uvuvale savanu vangu nu ngane va mwene uvisakhe ngane.  
\v 26 Khange yayiva ukhuta pala upwa khanchovivivwe kuvene, 'Umwe samlivanu vango,' pala vikhilangiwa 'vana va Nguluve umwumi.'”  
\v 27 Uyisaya ilila ukhukongano ni Israeli, “Ingave imbalilo ncha vana va Israeli ncha chivenchage ndu nganga ugwa nyanja, igiva gu melagalila legu giva masigalila uvu yavipokiwa.  
\v 28 Ulwakhuva unkuludeva ayikulitola ilimenyu lya mwene pakhanya pakhilunga, khimbivi nu uvukwilanile.  
\v 29 Nduvu Isaya vu anchovile, “Ingave unkuludeva vavasikhali sa khatulekhe khunsana kwu khivumbukho kyito, tukhale twiva ndu Sodoma, na tuvombivwa nda Mgomora.  
\v 30 twita khekhi lino? Ukhuta avanu va nkilunga uvu savalikhulonda uvwa yilweli, uvwa yilweli wa lwidincho.  
\v 31 Pwu lino unya Israeli, vyalikhulobda ululagilo lwe vwa yilweli sakhefikha.  
\v 32 Khekhi sayikhale ivwo? Ulwakhuva savalikhu nu lwidikho, valikholonde kwu mbombo. Vakhi khuvancha pakyanya paliwe ilya kwi kuvancho,  
\v 33 Nduvuyivile yisimbiwe, “Lola, nivikhile ilivwe lya kwi kuvancha mSayuni nu umwene uviikhwidikha salasukha.”   
\c 10
\cl Sura ya 10 
\p
\v 1 Valukolo inumbula yango nulwisayo lwango khwa Nguluve, khuvene khwa jili ya vupokhi, ukhuva nukhuvavula ukhuta, valene mbombo ya Nguluve sio kwa jili ya luhala.  
\v 2 Ukhuva ni khuvavula ukhuta vale nembombo ya Nguluve. Leno sio ukhuta valenu welewa.  
\v 3 Ukhuva Sara yemanyile ilweli ya Nguluve, vilonda ukhujenga elweli yavene vavo. savale videkhi khuvulyeu wa Nguluve.  
\v 4 Ukhuva uKlisite vitimilifu indagelo khuvulweli wakhila munu uvikhwami.  
\v 5 Ukhuva uMusa viasimbile ukhuhusu elweli ukhumana nululagelo: Umunu uvaivomba elweli ya lulagelo itamaga ni lwali iyi.”  
\v 6 Inava ilule yivonekha nu ulwidikho vun'cho lweli, “Usite ukhujova munumbula yakho, 'Vani ukhutoga khukianya?' (Khu khu ndata uKlisite pasi).  
\v 7 Usite ukho jova munumbula yakho veni a uvikhava ikhwikha pali guli iya yuyikhundata uKlisite khukhanya ukhuma khura fuile).  
\v 8 Lakini yijova khekhi? “Ilimonyu lelepipi nuve, mundomo gwakho na munumbula yakho.” Ilwo ni limenyu ilya lwidakho.” Lilyo tukholejova.  
\v 9 Ukhuva undomo gwakho gwipela khwa Yesu ukhuva vitwa, nukhwamini munumbula yakho ukhuta vu Nguluve ukhunchukha, wipona.  
\v 10 Ukhuva khunumbula umunu ikhedekha nukhupela lweli, na khundomo ukhupela nukhupokhela uvulokhole.  
\v 11 Ukhuva eliandikho linchova khila uvikhumwamini sakhasukha.”  
\v 12 Ukhuva lisikhuli lilyo salihwaninia Myahudi nu Myunani. ukhuva utwa yula yula vitwa vavoni vitayeli kuvoni avavikhumwilanga.  
\v 13 Ukhuva khila umunu uvikhule langela ilitawa lya Utwa ikhokhokha.  
\v 14 Khulitawa lilikhu viwesya ukhu mwilanga umwene vusava mpulikhi? liuvikhupulikha wasipali uvi lumbelela?  
\v 15 Vigaha ndati vawesya ukhulumbilila, vangasite ukusuhiwa? nduvuliandikhiwe.  
\v 16 Ukhuva voni savapulekheje ilimenyu ukhuva u Isaya ijova, “Utwa, veni uva pulikhe ilimenyu lieto?”  
\v 17 Ulwedekhe lukhuja ukhuhumila mulimenyu lya Klisite.  
\v 18 Leno nijova, “Lweli savakha pilikhe?” Lweli khabisa ilimenyu iyavene likhegile mughelunga khyoni na mamenyu gavene ukhuluta khu mwisio wa khelunga.  
\v 19 Khugoni, nijova, Lweli Israel sakhalumanye?” Ulwakhwanja u Musa akhajova, nukhuvan'chogosya ukhuvavikhila uwifu khuvanu vavo sio vataifa. Khujela yeyo sio ya vanu vataifa lelwo lejila vumanyi nikhuva nchonchela mpakha muvipe.”  
\v 20 Nu Isaya ikhifu fin'cho ukhujova, “Navonikha khuvala avasavakha kha ndo ndaga navonikhe khuvala vavo savalikhunogwa.”  
\v 21 Linu khuva Israeli ukhun'chova, “Isikhu joni nanyosinche amavokho gango khuvala avasavikhumulikha na khuvanu vango.”   
\c 11
\cl Sura ya 11 
\p
\v 1 Pu leino niita, pu, uNguluve avabeilile avanu vamwene? Ndeili na padebe. Ulwakhuva une nayune neili Mwisraeli, eikhivumbukhu khya Abrahamu, vakhikolo eikhya Benyamini.  
\v 2 UNguluve savabele avanu vamwene, uvuavamanyile ukhuhuma khuvulenguleilo. Pu samlumanyile uvuveige wiita khiikhi ukhukongana nu Eliya, umuasimeleihinche khwa uNguluve savuli ya Vaisraeli?  
\v 3 “Ntwa vavabudile avasuhwa vakho, navene vanchinanginie inekhelo nchakho, une nei mwene nene niesiigile, navene vilonda uwumi wango.”  
\v 4 Pu uwamule wa Nguluve wiita khiikhi khyulyuve? “Neileiveikhile savuli yango avaalufu saba yango avusavikhufugameela amafugamilo uBaali.”  
\v 5 Paninie neiyo, usiekhe ugu leino pu khuvaale uvuvasigile savu ya vuhale wa luhungu.  
\v 6 Pui leino yiengave savuli ya luhungu, pusayiva mumivombele. pu apo uluhungu pusalwiva luhungu.  
\v 7 Khyu khinu khikhi leino? eikhyu uIsrael alikhulonda, sakhivone, pu avahaliwa vakhiwene, na vaange vakhasya.  
\v 8 Nduvuyeisimbiwe: “Unguluve avapile einumbula eiyavubungefu, amiho ukhula valekhe ukhulola, ni mbulukhutu ukhuta valekhe ukhupuleikha, pupakha eilelo eiye.”  
\v 9 Vape uDaudi iita, “Nchilekhe imesa nchavo nchive nyaafu, neimitego gwa khwipeinja, nukhwitavuleila khuvene.  
\v 10 Galekhe amiho gavo gave niehisi pu valekhe ukhulola. Ukhavinamye emisana gyavo khitaduga.”  
\v 11 Leino niita, “Puvei, kuvinche nu khugwa?” Yelekhe ukhuva ewo lusikhu. Puleino ukhulemwa khwa veene, uvupokhi vufikhe khuvapanji, ukhuta avene vavo vavone wifu.  
\v 12 Leino einave ukhulemwa khwavo vukaviwa khilunga, nu puyiengave uvufuve waavo vukavi wavapanji, pukhigelelo khiekhi eikhilutelile puyeve khunkwila nila khwavo?  
\v 13 Na leino leino ninchova numwe mwie vunu va panji, neivile isuhwa khuvanu avajilunga ifinge, nikhigineihincha eimbombo ya vutangeli wango.  
\v 14 Pamo yanikhuvapela uwifu avaleimbeili gumo nune, pano ya tukhuvapokha vaninie.  
\v 15 Pu eingave ukhubeliwa khwavo lweideha no lwa khilunga, ukhyupeileiliwa khwavo ya khwiva ndakhikhi pu uwumi uwakhuhuma khuvunchukha?  
\v 16 Einave isekhe itanchi khibana vuyileiwo khu nongeya vutine. Einave undela khibana pu amasasi nagope wuwuwa.  
\v 17 Pu einave amasasi maninie gageidewe, uve, lisasi lya msitu lya Mzeituni, ugugwavyaliwe muvene nu pungave waleepyo paninie navene eimilela gya vukani wa Mizeituni.  
\v 18 Ulekhe ukhwiginia mumasasi, pu unave vukhiginia saveve yuve vukhugitanga emilela, pu emilela gikhukhutanga uve.  
\v 19 Puleino ayawita, “Amaswato gagidiewe ukhuta neivuliwe mukhikolo.  
\v 20 Eiyo lweli, savuli ya khusita ukhwideekha khwavo vagedeiwe, pu uve wa eimile ulukangafu savuli ya lweideikho lwakho. Ulekhe ukwisageila yuve pakyanya fincho pu dwaadage.  
\v 21 Pu ulwakhuva eingave uNguluve sagalekhe lenche amaswato amatengule, sakha khuhigile uve na yuve.  
\v 22 Lola, leino, imbombo inonu nu vukali wa Nguluve. Khuluvafu lumo, uvukali wa inchile khuva yuta vala avagwile. Pu khuluvafu ulunge, uluhungu lwa Nguluve lukhwincha palyuve ungave yawinchiga muvunonu wa mwene. Einave ate uve nayuveayavubeiliwa.  
\v 23 Na eingave savakhendelelage mukhusitakhwideekha kwavo, yavi valiwa khange. Ulwa khuva uNguluve alei na makha agakhuvyaleila khange.  
\v 24 Pu ulwakhuva umwe mungave mwageidewe khunji khugugwa gwa mbutengulielo Mzeituni gwa msitu, puleino eikyavulenguleilo khileivunge Mzeituni unonu pu sayiva fiva ukhulutilila fincho ava yuta?  
\v 25 Ulwa khuva valokolo saninogwa msite ughulumanya ukhukongana ukhu kongana nei siri eiye, ukhuta mulekhe ukhuva nu luhala mumisagiele gyienyo yumwe. Ei siri eiye khukhuta uvukafu vuhumile mu Israeli, imakha ukhunchikwilanila khwa filunga yakhiva khwinchile.  
\v 26 Puleino ava Israeli vooni yavipokhiwa, ndu unyeisimbiwe: “Ukhuhuma khu Sayuni ikhwincha upokhi, pu ayihencha uvuvivi ukhuhuma khwa Yakobo.  
\v 27 Na eili puyaliva ndagano pu paninie na veene useikhi uguyakhiva nihencha imbivi nchaavo.”  
\v 28 Khuluvafu lumo ukhu kongana neilivangeili, vivipeiliwa savuli yienyo. Khuluvafu ulunge ukhukonga na vuhale wa Nguluve, vavyaliwe savuli ya vankukhu yavo.  
\v 29 Ulwa khuv uluhombo ni nyeilango yu Nguluve sayigevukha.  
\v 30 Ulwakhuva pakhwanda umwe mwale vagolo va Nguluve, puleino mulyupeilile uluhungu lwa Nguluve savuli ya khugalukha kwavo.  
\v 31 Khunjila yeiyeiyo, leino ava yuta ava vagalwikhe, pu eilyu leivonikhe khukhuta savuli ya khisa ikyu muhungukhiwe umwe mvahile ukhwambeilila uluhungu.  
\v 32 Ulwakhuva uNguluve avadeindile avanu vooni muvugalukhi, ukhuta pwava vonele eikhisa vooni.  
\v 33 Umunchi velile mbaha uvukavi nu luhungu nu vumanyi wa Nguluve! Savunchingakhimchi wa uvuheigi wa mwene, ni njeila ncha mwene sanchi manyikhikha!  
\v 34 “Pu veini uvyakhavu manyile uvufumbwe wantwa? puveini va masago khumwene?  
\v 35 Pu veini taasi agelieli ukhupa eikhinu uNguluve pu ahombiwe khange?”  
\v 36 Ulwa khuva ukhuhuma khumwene, na khunjila ya mwene na khumwene, ifinu fyooni pufile, khumwene luve ludwando isikhu nchooni. Amina.   
\c 12
\cl Sura ya 12 
\p
\v 1 Mwi evalunkidwangwa, niekhuvadova, khukhisa ikya Nguluve, muhumyie eimivieli gyienyo yieve nekhelo ienyumi, imbalanche, iyienoghelanile pamiho agha Nguluve. Ulwa lwu lyesayo lyenyo ulunonu.  
\v 2 Mlakhikhonga ikheilunga eikhi, musyetukhe ukhuva vapya vamusango ghienyo. Muyiemanye eilweli iyalugano ulwa Nguluve uluunonu, ulunoghelaniele nukhwidihana.  
\v 3 Ulwa khuva ulusayo uluniekhaviele nikhumbula khila munu uvyaliekhulyumwe alekhage ukhunchova amavaha aghalutilile nduvugakhanughiwagwa, avinchage nukhwilola nukhuduga, nduvu uNguluve aghavile khila munu eikhighavilo lyueidikho.  
\v 4 Nduvuwu umbieli ghumu ghuliniefi ifilungielo fingi, ifilunghili ifi safiliene imbombo yeimo.  
\v 5 Nayufye tulievinigi, tulie umbieli ghumo mwa Klisiti, na yufwe khila munu alienikhilungielo ikya mwene khunine.  
\v 6 Tulinifikhungielwa ifisafi hwanine khiela munu ukhukhongana nulusayo ulutukhavile.  
\v 7 Tungave mukhutangiela tutangielage, avanyakhumanyisya vamanyisyaghe.  
\v 8 Unya khuvunga, avungaghe, unyanumbula ienonu avombaghe khunumbula, uvilongoncha alongonchaghe na makha, unyakhisa avoneisyaghe ulukheghelo.  
\v 9 Ulughano lulekhaghe ukhuva lwa vudetelenchi; uliekhalalielaghe ielivivi, wibatieliele eilinonu.  
\v 10 Muughananage yumwe khulughano ulwa khilukholo. Khulughano muvalongonchaghe ava yienyo.  
\v 11 Mlekhaghe ukhuva voolo, muvinchaghe nukwiyumilincha, munumbula vumukhumbombela Untwa.  
\v 12 Khuluhuvielo, muhovokhaghe mumbupala vumupuliekhiela, mukyiesaya, mwieyumilienchage.  
\v 13 Vukhundiwa khuvavalanche vumunkhonga uvudekhedekhe, ukhuvupieliela avagheni mwintangaghe.  
\v 14 Muvasayaghe avikhuvaviphiencha; muvasayaghe mulekhe ukhuva kholola.  
\v 15 Muhovokhaghe navihovokha numwe, mulielaghe naviliela numwe.  
\v 16 Muphuliehanaghe mutamaghe ndunonchehencho navayienyo. Mlekhaghe ukwieghienia, muvinchage vanu vakhuvatanga avalemilwe. Khange mlekhaghe ukwieghinia ukhuta mukhimanyile khila khinu.  
\v 17 Mulekhaghe ukhung'omba umunu uvuvivi khu khuvuvivi. Muvombaghe inonu pha miho ghavanu voni.  
\v 18 Ulwa khuva uluvafu ulunghe khulyumwe, muntamaghe nulunonchehencho na vanu voni.  
\v 19 Vaghane, mulekhage ukhuhomba imbivi, hange muhenaghe uluviepho lwa Nguluve. Ulwa khuva liesimbiwe, 'Uluhombo luliepakyanya palyune; Une nielahomba,' inchova Untwa.”  
\v 20 “Khumbe unduguu vako angave nienjala undiesye. Angave nikyumiela, inywesye. Ulwa khuva ukhughaha eiwo wiva vukhuntumiela amakhalasiela agha mwoto pantwe pamwene.”  
\v 21 Vulekhaghe ukhukhutola uvuvivi, humbe vulemwaghe uvuvivi khuvunonu.   
\c 13
\cl Sura ya 13 
\p
\v 1 Khila munu eidikhaghe khuvantwa avavaha, ulwa khuva vusikhuli uvuntwa uvusawihuma khwa Nguluve. Uvuntwa woni uvupwuvule wihuma khwa Nguluve.  
\v 2 Hange uvieibela khu vantwa pwu ikhilana nululaghilo ulwa Nguluve; voope aviekhilana valakhava uvuhieghi.  
\v 3 Ulwa khuva avantwa savidwancha khuvanu avivomba inonu, vidwancha khuvanu avivomba imbivi. Pwu wienogwa ulekhe ukhiwadwada avantwa? Pwu uvombaghe inonu vope pwu iekhukhughiniaga.  
\v 4 Ulwa khuva avilongoncha vavombi va Nguluve ukhuvomba inonu. Hange ungavombaghe imbivi, pwu udwade, ulwa khuva sawighegha eimundu vuvule. Umwene vie mbombi va Nguluve, unsuhiwa va Nguluve viivomba ukhuvunga khuvala avivomba imbivi.  
\v 5 Khoumbe tuvankhongaghe ukhuviediekha avalongonchi, tulekhe ukhuwada uluvungo lulwa yaluhumila, khaumbe khumasago gheitu.  
\v 6 Pwu musonga eisongo. ulwa khuva avantwa vavombi va Nguluve, vavo unsiekhi gwoni vivomba imbombo eiyakhulongoncha.  
\v 7 Umpinchaghe khila munu khiekyo ikhikhumela: ungave vudayiwa iesongo ukhasonge; inave khusongencha ukhasongenche, uvinogiewa uvudwanchi, iindwanchi, uvie ilondiwa eilisima weimphe ielisima.  
\v 8 Ulekhe ukhuva nunkhole numunu, mughananaghe, ulwa khuva uvianghanile uniene iva ankhongile ululaghilo.  
\v 9 Ukhunchova ukhuta, “Ulalieghupagha, ulahienchagha, ulabudagha, ulanogwagwa,” inave pwunchile iindagielo inchiinghe nchihangile mululagielo ulu lumo: “Ughane uvyaliepawipi nuve nduvuwieghanile yuve.”  
\v 10 Ulughano salukhumbomba uvyalipwipwi nuve uvuvivi, ulughano lulwidihiene nululaghilo ulwa ndaghilo.  
\v 11 Ena, tungaluma ukhuta unsiekhi, ugwa khusisimukha ukhuhuma mumbuughono uwa tulu gwinchile. Ulwa khuva uvupokhi wieto vuliepawiephi nufwe upwu tukhatengwile ukhumwiedikha.  
\v 12 Eikhilo yiepienchighe eno, eimusi yieheghelile. Pwu tufule imbombo inchamuhisi, tufwale ifilweilo ifya lumuli.  
\v 13 Umuyiekhuvelile iemusi, vutuvinchage eiwo nukhusana, tulavichagha nuntoli, nuvughanchi, khuvulyasi nuvulieghu, ukhulekha ukhulwa niekhitule.  
\v 14 Pwu tumfwale Untwa uYesu Klisiti, tulekhaghe ukhulola umbieli, nukhukhonga uvunogwe uwa mbieli.   
\c 14
\cl Sura ya 14 
\p
\v 1 Umwene uvyalienulwiedikho lupepe, mung'eghelehenchage, mulekhaghe ukhung'iegha amasago aga mwene.  
\v 2 Umunu yuomo alienulywidiekho, ilya fyoni, hange undekhedekhe ilya eimboga.  
\v 3 Umwene uvieilya alekhaghe ukhumbeda yuywa silya. Hange yuywa silya alekhaghe ukhungiegha yuywa ilya. Ulwa khuva uNguluve amwidikhile.  
\v 4 Uve veve veni yuve vukhung'iegha umbombi uyuonge? Khumbaha vamwene yuywa umwene ikwiema apange igwa. Mwene, ulwa khuva Untwa iwesya ukhumwimiekha.  
\v 5 Umunu yumo ivomba nchincho sajinchinogelanile khila lienchuva. Uyuonge ivona amachuva ghoni ghalihanile. Khila munu alumanyaghe munduhala lwa mwene yuywa.  
\v 6 Umwene uvieikhuyimiekha ielinchuva, ikhumwiemiekha unkhuludeva, vope uvieilya ilya khunkuludeva. Hange uviesilya, silya khunkuludeva, hange vope ienkhunsana uNguluve.  
\v 7 Ulwa khuva asikhuli umunu munghati ndyufwe uvieitama mumakha ghamwene, hanghe asikhuli uvivomba mumakha aghamwene yuywa.  
\v 8 Ulwa khuva inave tutama, tutama khu nkhuludeva, apange tunghafwe, tuliekyuma kya Nkuludeva.  
\v 9 Ulwa khuva uKlisiti afwile hange akhava mwumi, pwu avile inkhuludeva va voni avafwile na vumi voni.  
\v 10 Uve pwu khekhi, vukhung'iegha ulukhololwo vakho? Aphanghe uve khekhi, mbona vukhumbeda ulukhololwo? Ulwa khuva ufwe twivoni tuleima pavulongolo pakhighoda ikyavukhighi ikya Nguluve.  
\v 11 Ulwa khuva lisimbiwe, “Nduvinietama,” ienchova unkhuludeva, “Khila lifughamielo lilafughama pawlongolo palyune.”  
\v 12 Ulwa khuva ewo, khila munu alahumya indaghielo incha mwene pavulongolo pa Nguluve.  
\v 13 Pwu twielekhelwe ukhuhieghana, huba tukhenche uvuhieghi uwu, umunu alekhaghe ukhuviekha ikhienu ikya khumbiepiencha ulukololwe au eikyakhugwiesya.  
\v 14 Nilumanyile hanghe undienganiche mwa Yesu Klisiti, ukhuta khisikhuli eikhinu iekhivivi, khumwene ikhienu khiela khivivi.  
\v 15 Ulukhololyo angave nuluviepho niekyakhulya, alulekhile ulughano. Khu kyakhula kyakho ulekhe unkhunanga umunu yuywa uKlisiti afwile khunongwa incha mwene.  
\v 16 Humbe uvunonu wienyo vulekhe ukhutambuliwa khuvivi.  
\v 17 Ulwa khuva uludeva lwa Nguluve salwakhulya aphange ukhunywa, pwu wayilweli nu lunonchekhencho nuluhekhelo mwu mepo umbalanche.  
\v 18 Ulwa khuva uveikhumbombela uKlisiti mumbombo incho inkhung'ovosya uNguluve hange iekwidiekhiwa na vanu.  
\v 19 Yiengave ewo, munkhonge imbombo inchalunonchencho ni mbombo inchilondiwa ukhwimiekhana.  
\v 20 Khunongwa iyakyakhula ulekhe ukhunanga imbombo ya Nguluve. Lweli fyoni finonu, fiva fivivi khumunu uvieilya nukwihiega.  
\v 21 Lwiva lunonu ukhulekha ukhulya ienyama nukhunywa uvueghiembie hange nukhuvomba ikhinu khikyo ulukhololyo vakho khikhundemancha.  
\v 22 Ulwiedikho lulwa ulienalwo munumbula yakho luve lwakho pavulongolo pha Nguluve. Amebairkiwa umunu uviesikhihigha mumbwumi wa mwene khulimenyu lielyo alilyedikhe.  
\v 23 Hange yuywa sidiekhe ikwilamwa, angalye, ahieghiwe ukhuta alie nienongwa, ulwa khuva akhalile pasita kwidikha. Khila mbombo iyievombiwa vulusipali ulwiedikho wiva vutulanongwa.   
\c 15
\cl Sura ya 15 
\p
\v 1 Panogile yufwe tuliena makha tupiembe uvuvivi wa vavo valievavule amakha.  
\v 2 Khila munu mughati umwu panoghile ukhunoghele paninie uvyali pawipi nu mwene, upielile uvunonu akhavombeliwe.  
\v 3 Ulwa khuva uKlisiti vope sakhanoghele mwene. Nduvuliesimbiwe, “Amadusi uguvakhakhudukhile uve nikhaghupielile une.”  
\v 4 Ulwa khuva ghoni aghatalile ughusimbiwa ghasimbiwe ukhuta tumanyilaghe ufwe, ukhuta tuvinchaghe nukhununala nulunonchekhencho ulwa vusimbe tukhave ukhununala.  
\v 5 UNguluve uvyalie nuluhuvilo nukhununancha avatange ukhunchova pwu paninie yuomwe khwa yuomwe ukhungonga uKlisiti uYesu.  
\v 6 Khunumbula yeimo na khundamo guumo muve vakhughinia uNguluve Udada va Nkhuludeva veitu uYesu Klisiti.  
\v 7 Pwu mwupielilanilage yumwe khwa yumwe, nduvu uYesu Klisiti avupielile, ukhuta uNguluve aghiniwagwe.  
\v 8 Ulwa khuva ninchova niita uKlisiti avombikhe intangieli va kwiedihana ukhukhegheta pavuyielweli uwa Nguluve. Ukhuta nchidulukhe iendaghilo inchuvapokhile avadada veto,  
\v 9 hange ukhuta avanyampanji vamwiemikhaghe uNguluve khu khisa kya mwene. Nduvuliesimbiwe, “Ulwa khuva nilakhusana pa vanyapanji nune nielemba ilitawa lyakho.”  
\v 10 Hange ninchova, “Muhovokhaghe, mwievapanji, pwu paninie navanu avamwene.”  
\v 11 Hange, “Umwe mwievanyapanji, munghiniaghe unkhuludeva, umwe mwievanu mwivono mumwiedikhaghe.”  
\v 12 Hange u Isaya inchova, “Khila khumila ikhikho ikya Yese, umwene vyalaluta khulongoncha. Avanyapanji vu avanyapanji vikhunguvilagha.”  
\v 13 Umwene uNguluve vivaluhuvilo avadienche ulunonchehencho mukhwidikha, mughendelelaghe nduhuvielo, mu makha agha Mepo umbalanche.  
\v 14 Valukholo lwango nikhuvavula ukhuta nielumanyile ukhuva mudieghile ulughano. Mulienuluhala lwoni hange mukhiemanyile ukhuvungana.  
\v 15 Hange nikhuvasiembiela ukwietanga uluvafu ulwa kalata iyie, nikhuvakhumbusya khulusayo ulunupielile khwa Nguluve.  
\v 16 Ukhuva nive munu valutanghielo khuvanyapanji, nielievombele ielivangili ilya Nguluve imbombo iya vutekhenchi, ukhuva avanyapanji vave nekhelo iyiediekhiwe, yienga valanchiwe nu Mepo umbalanche.  
\v 17 Khumbe nienoghile ukwieghienia mwa Klisiti u Yesu pavulongolo pa Nguluve.  
\v 18 Ulwa khuva saniekhaghele ukhutambula eilimenyu lielyo savombile uKlisiti khu mbombo yango, avapanji viedikhaghe khumamenyu na khumbombo,  
\v 19 khumakha aghakhuvonesya ifidegho, mu makha agha Mepo umbalanche. Ukhuhuma khu Yerusalemu, na mundokhanji khanji, ukhudugha khu ililiko nimalile ukhulumbilila eilivangili ilya Klisiti khuvuvalanche.  
\v 20 Nienghetange ukhulumbilila ielivanghieli, nielekhe ukhulumbiliela upwu ilitawa ilya Klisiti vamalile ukhulitambula, ulwa khuva uyuninchengagha mundwuto ulwa munu uyuonghe.  
\v 21 Bakho nduvuliesimbiwe ukhuta, khuvala vavo savalie phulikhe ielimenyu ilya mwene vikhulievonagha, hange vavo savalumbielieliwe viekhulimanyagha.”  
\v 22 Inchi nchunchikhaviekhile ukhuta une vansighaghe ukwincha khulyumwe.  
\v 23 Ukhuva lino, nielievuvule unsiekhi khunu, hanghe iemyakha minghi nikhale nuvufumbwe uwakhwincha khulyumwe.  
\v 24 Unsiekhi gwoni ugwakhiva nieluta khu Hispania, (pwu yunikwincha khulyumwe) ulwa khuva nihuvila ukhuvavona umwe vunighenda nu khukheliekhiwa numwe, enumbula yango yighute khulyumwe padebe.  
\v 25 Leino niluta tasi ku Yerusalemu nikhavatange avanyapanji.  
\v 26 Ulwakhu panoghile khuvanu avakhu Makedonia nava Akaya ukhuvomba ukhuhanghilanila khuva vavalanche avaliekhu Yerusalemu vavo vaghanchu.  
\v 27 Ena, panogile, hange vavile nuonkhole khuvene. Ulwa khuva avanyapanji vahangile ukhuvomba imbo inchavene incha munumbula, panoghile ukhuvavombela imbombo inchavene incha mbielie.  
\v 28 Pwu ninghamale imbombo eiyo, nukhuviekha ikhimanyilo isekhe ieyo, nighendela khulyumwe, ukhuluta khu Hispania.  
\v 29 Une nilumanyile ukhuta nienhinche khulyumwe, nikwincha nikhuvagheghela ulusayo ulwa Klisiti.  
\v 30 Valukholo lwango, nikhuvadovela khu Untwa veitu u Yesu Klisiti, nulughano ulya Mepo, mwietangaghe pwu paninie nune ukhundovela khwa Nguluve.  
\v 31 Ukhuta niepokhiwe paninie navala avasavikwiedhikha khu Yudea, hanghe uvuvombeli wango uvunielienawo khu Yerusalemu wiedhiekhiewe na vavalanche.  
\v 32 Pwu nienche khulyumwe nuluhekhelo, nduvuinogwa uNguluve, pwu nikhaghatalukhe paninie numwe.  
\v 33 UNguluve uvalunonchehencho avinchaghe numwe mwevoni. Amina   
\c 16
\cl Sura ya 16 
\p
\v 1 Nikhuvapa umwe uFibi ulumkholo lwienyo umbombi va ntembiela iya khu Kenkrea,  
\v 2 mumwupilile munditawa ilya Ntwa. Nduvupanoghile mwievavalanche, mukhantanghe imbombo nchoni ienchakhiva inogwa ukhuta muntangaghe umwe. Ulwa khuva umwene akhale intanghili va vanu avingi, akhanangha nayune.  
\v 3 Mumponiaghe u Priska nu Akila, vavombaghe imbombo nune mwa Klisiti uYesu,  
\v 4 vakhiedikhe ukhughiediwa eimintwa khumbombo yango. Une nikhuvasana, saniekhuvasana ywone nie mwene naghiemipelela na vanyapanji voni.  
\v 5 Mumonehenchaghe nie ntembile iyielie munyumba yavene. Mumponie uEpanieto, ughane vangho, yuywa avile nekhelo ya Asia khwa Klisiti.  
\v 6 Mumponie uMariamu ivyahayiekhe eino khunongwa yeinyo.  
\v 7 Mumponie u Androniko Yunia, avamanyani vango vavo tukhakhunghiwe pwu paninie nune, vavo vakhabeliwe muvankhonghi, vuvakhale mwa Klisiti une vusanietengwiele.  
\v 8 Mumponie uAmpliato, ughane vango mu Ntwa.  
\v 9 Mumponie u Urbano, umbomba mbombo paninie nune mwa Klisiti.  
\v 10 Mumponie u Apele, umwene iediekhiwa mwa Yesu Klisiti. Mumonehenche na vanu avalimunyumba iya Aristobulo.  
\v 11 Mumponie u Helodiani, umanyani vango, muvaponie avanu avaliemunyumba eiya Nalkiso, vavo valie mu Ntwa.  
\v 12 Mumponie u Tlifaina nu Tlifosa, yuywa akhitangi mu Ntwa,  
\v 13 Mumponie u Lufo, uvyahaliwe nu Nunkhuludeva, nuvanina, yuywa vi jyuva vango nayune.  
\v 14 Mumponie u Asinklito, Flegon, Helme, Patloba, Helima, na valukholo lwango voni vavo valiepwu panienie na vene.  
\v 15 Mumponighe u Filologo nu Yulia, nu Nerea nu ng'anchave, nu Olimpa, na vavalanche voni vavo valiepwu paninie.  
\v 16 Mwieponighe pakhiefuva ikhighatalufu. Mumpelela gwoni ugwa Klisiti muvaponiage.  
\v 17 Valukholo lwango, nikhuvadova, mwielolehge khuvala avisonghelehania nie mbombo inchakhulemencha ukhusyetula ulumanyisyo ulumanyile. Muvinchaghe pavutali navo avanu avo.  
\v 18 Ulwa khuva avanu ava savikhumbombela Untwa veitu uYesu Klisiti, vivombele amatumbu ghavene vavo. Khumamenyu amadekhedekhe khanghe aghanoghile vuvikhesyova vene munumbula inchavanu avagholofu.  
\v 19 Ulwa khuva uwiedhiehinchi wienyo vufikhe khuvanu voni. Pwu niehovokha khulyumwe, hanghe ninogwa umwe muve vanu va luhala ukhuvomba imbombo ienonu, nukhuva vakhonyofu khumbombo imbivi.  
\v 20 UNguluve uvalunonchehencho vieikhumwibatagha undughu na mbievie pasi pamalunde ghienyo. Ulusayo lwantwa veito uYesu Klisiti nuvinchaghe paninie numwe.  
\v 21 U Timotheo, umbomba mbombo nune, ikhuvaponia, nu Lukio, nu Yasoni nu Sospeter, avamanyani vango.  
\v 22 Une, nie Teltio, nene nisiembile ibalula iyie, nikhuvaponia munditawa ilyantwa.  
\v 23 U Gayo, yuywa akhamokhile mu mpelela yoni ikhuvaponia. U Elasito, uvieilolela uvunchenge, ikhuvaponia, nayu Kwalto ulukhololwe.  
\v 24 (Ulusayo lwa Ntwa vetu uYesu Klisiti luvinchaghe numwe mwievoni. Ameni.”  
\v 25 Lino aghiniwagwe umwene uviikhuvapa amakha aghalihanile nielivangili ilyango ukhundumbilila uYesu Klisiti, ukhukhwanana nuluvonekhelo ulukhafihime lukhale khuvutitu ukhuhuma khatale ukhusila lusikhu,  
\v 26 lukhavonekha khusiekhi ughu khuvusiembe uwa vanyamalago, vukhavonekha khuvanyapanji voni ukhuta wanchovile uNguluve vakhusila lusikhu, ukhuta viedikhile ulwiedhiekho.  
\v 27 Vie Nguluve unyakhisa mwene, uvuntwa alienawo uYesu Klisiti, ukhusila lusikhu. Amina   